%26quot%3BThat's%20where%20you%20want%20to%20be%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20the%20top%20of%20the%20ziggurat%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BEverybody's%20trying%20to%20get%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman's%20partnership%20dates%20back%20to%20a%20time%20when%20its%20leaders%20contributed%20their%20own%20capital%20to%20help%20run%20the%20firm.%20The%20company%20is%20now%20publicly%20traded%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frip-goldman-sachs-wall-street-investment-bank-dead-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eits%20partnership%20still%20carries%20influence%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20perks%20alone%20make%20it%20enough%20to%20salivate%20over%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20a%20base%20salary%20of%20about%20%241%20million%20per%20year%2C%20which%20can%20swell%20by%20multiples%20when%20factoring%20in%20year-end%20bonus%20comp.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20coming%20months%2C%20Citigroup%2C%20Morgan%20Stanley%2C%20Bank%20of%20America%2C%20and%20more%20will%20also%20announce%20the%20newest%20members%20of%20their%20top%20ranks%2C%20who%20usually%20carry%20the%20title%20of%20managing%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20spoke%20to%20Argenti%20and%20a%20former%20partner%20at%20Goldman%20to%20get%20a%20look%20inside%20the%20partnership%20promotion%20process%2C%20from%20what%20it%20takes%20to%20make%20the%20grade%20to%20the%20perks%20and%20privileges%20that%20come%20with%20the%20title.%20They%20also%20shed%20light%20on%20what%20this%20year's%20class%20might%20look%20like%20and%20what%20its%20makeup%20could%20say%20about%20the%20priorities%20of%20the%20150-year-old%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaking%20partner%20at%20Goldman%20Sachs%20is%20a%20rigorous%20and%20competitive%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20Goldman%20spokesperson%20Tony%20Fratto%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BNo%20one%20outside%20of%20our%20firm%20or%20the%20partnership%20has%20any%20insight%20into%20what%20decisions%20will%20be%20made.%20If%20you've%20hear