s%20hardly%20right%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETo%20make%20their%20wish%20fairer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20man%20finding%20a%20centipede%20in%20a%20meal%20served%20in%20the%20IRCTC's%20VIP%20lounge%20should%20%26quot%3Bcause%20the%20Railways%20some%20disorder%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20wrote%2C%20while%20another%20poem%20commented%20on%20New%20Zealand%20imposing%20a%20three-minute%20cap%20on%20farewell%20hugs%20at%20airports.%20Mr%20Debroy%20gave%20a%20sartorial%20twist%20to%20the%20bizarre%2C%20from%20a%20man%20running%20a%20fake%20court%20in%20Ahmedabad%20for%20five%20years%20to%20a%20Greek%20man%20sneaking%20into%20his%20neighbour's%20house%20to%20smell%20their%20shoes%20to%20a%20UK%20minister%20wanting%20to%20give%20obese%20people%20weight-loss%20injections%20to%20get%20them%20back%20to%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EToday's%20Mint%20Metric%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flivemint%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40livemint%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnHyderabad's%20food%20safety%20team%3Cbr%3E%5CnHas%20findings%20to%20make%20you%20scream.%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20hotels%20and%20eateries%20around%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnRats%20and%20cockroaches%20abound%2C%3Cbr%3E%5CnClearly%20a%20parasite's%20dream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Bibek%20Debroy%20(%40bibekdebroy)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbibekdebroy%2Fstatus%2F1848212817427451986%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2021%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Debroy%2C%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Economic%20Advisory%20Council%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India%2C%20who%20died%20on%20Friday%20at%20the%20age%20of%2069%2C%20was%20celebrated%20for%20his%20extensive%20contributions%20to%20economic%20policy%20and%20research.%20The%20Bengali%20boy%20from%20Shillong%2C%20whose%20parents%20migrated%20from%20Bangladesh%2C%20studied%20from%20Delhi%20School%20of%20Economics%20and%20Trinity%20College%2C%20Cambridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20theoretical%20and%20empirical%20economist%2C%20his%20contributions%20spanned%20the%20game%20theory%2C%20income%20inequality%2C%20poverty%2C%20legal%20reforms%2C%20and%20railway%20policy.%20From%201993%20to%201998%2C%20he%20served%20as%20Director%20of%20a%20Ministry%20of%20Finance%20and%20UNDP%20project%20on%20legal%20reforms%2C%20and%20in%201994-95%2C%20he%20worked%20with%20the%20Department%20of%20Economic%20Affairs.%20Since%20its%20inception%2C%20Debroy%20was%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20NITI%20Aayog%2C%20the%20government's%20primary%20think%20tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Debroy%20chaired%20the%20Finance%20Ministry's%20'Expert%20Committee%20for%20Infrastructure%20Classification%20and%20Financing%20Framework%20for%20Amrit%20Kaal%2C'%20an%20initiative%20to%20elevate%20India's%20economic%20standing%20over%20the%20next%2025%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20served%20as%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Railways%20Ministry's%20high-powered%20committee%20on%20restructuring%20the%20country's%20lifeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20think%20tank%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20Institute%20for%20Contemporary%20Studies%20(RGICS)%2C%20where%20he%20served%20between%201997%20and%202005%2C%20a%20report%20published%20under%20him%20during%20then%20prime%20minister%20Manmohan%20Singh's%20tenure%20put%20Gujarat%20at%20the%20top%20of%20an%20index%20measuring%20economic%20freedom.%20Amid%20unease%20in%20the%20Congress%20and%20an%20ensuing%20heated%20debate%20on%20the%20Gujarat%20model%20of%20development%2C%20Mr%20Debroy%20moved%20to%20the%20Punjab%20Haryana%20Delhi%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%2C%20following%20the%20two-year%20stint%20there%20by%20a%20long%20stint%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20Policy%20and%20Research%20from%202007.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20teaching%20career%20included%20stints%20at%20Presidency%20College%2C%20Kolkata%20(1979-83)%2C%20Gokhale%20Institute%20of%20Politics%20and%20Economics%2C%20Pune%20(1983-87)%2C%20and%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Foreign%20Trade%2C%20Delhi%20(1987-93).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20bibliography%20includes%20three%20books%20centered%20on%20economics%2C%20one%20among%20them%20'Getting%20India%20Back%20on%20Track%3A%20An%20Action%20Agenda%20for%20Reform'.%20It%20highlighted%20the%20significance%20of%20contestation%20and%20participation%20as%20a%20counter%20to%20%26quot%3BIndia's%20primordial%20nationalisms%26quot%3B%2C%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bauthentically%20and%20indisputably%20Indian%26quot%3B%20creation%20of%20a%20multi-layered%20political%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDabbling%20in%20the%20themes%20of%20spirituality%20and%20mythology%2C%20Mr%20Debroy's%20collection%20of%20around%2050%20authored%20books%20includes%2043%20translations%20of%20various%20Indian%20texts%2C%20most%20aimed%20at%20keeping%20them%20accessible%20and%20relevant%20for%20the%20youth.%20He%20translated%20the%20unabridged%20version%20of%20the%20Mahabharata%20into%20English%2C%20in%20a%20series%20of%2010%20volumes.%20This%20apart%2C%20he%20also%20translated%20the%20Puranas%2C%20the%20four%20Vedas%2C%20the%20Bhagvad%20Gita%20and%2011%20major%20Upanishads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20in%20his%20book%20The%20Bhagavad%20Gita%20For%20Millennials%2C%20he%20had%20written%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20who%20has%20not%20repeatedly%20heard%20and%20studied%20the%20Gita%2C%20yet%20desires%20liberation%2C%20will%20be%20laughed%20at%20by%20children.%20But%20those%20who%20hear%20it%20and%20study%20it%20are%20not%20humans.%20They%20are%20certainly%20like%20the%20Gods.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20his%20recent%20book%20steers%20away%20from%20the%20theme.%20Inked%20in%20India%20documents%20the%20entirety%20of%20recognised%20fountain%20pen%2C%20nib%2C%20and%20ink%20manufacturers%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Congress%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20called%20Mr%20Debroy%20a%20%26quot%3Bthought-provoking%20commentator%26quot%3B%20on%20public%20issues%20beyond%20economics.%20Union%20Minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%20remembered%20his%20enriching%20newspaper%20columns.%20Debroy%20also%20anchored%20'Itihasa'%2C%20a%20show%20telecast%20on%20Sansad%20TV.%20The%20series%20explored%20what%20is%20%26quot%3BBharata%26quot%3B%2C%20what%20it%20means%20to%20be%20%26quot%3BBhartiya%26quot%3B%20and%20what%20it%20means%20in%20terms%20of%20India's%20Sanatana%20tradition.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730453820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-09%2Fbibek-debroy-650_650x400_61506405195.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbeyond-an-economist-and-author-dr-bibek-debroys-cheeky-twist-to-bizarre-incidents-6920906%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Padma%20Shri%20awardee%20Dr%20Bibek%20Debroy%20donned%20many%20hats%20-%20an%20economist%2C%20political%20commentator%2C%20author%2C%20translator%2C%20educator%20and%20a%20television%20anchor.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbeyond-an-economist-and-author-dr-bibek-debroys-cheeky-twist-to-bizarre-incidents-6920906%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20California%20couple%20built%20a%20%24500%2C000%20ADU%20in%20their%20parents'%20backyard%20when%20they%20couldn't%20afford%20to%20buy%20a%20traditional%20house%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225529%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aislyn%20(left)%20and%20Ali%20Benjamin%20(right)%20on%20the%20porch%20of%20their%20ADU.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F671ff40ca0a0cc14f22474cc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223828%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAli%20Benjamin%2C%20left%2C%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Aislyn%2C%20built%20an%20ADU%20in%20the%20Bay%20Area%20as%20their%20first%20home.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Villa%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAislyn%20and%20Ali%20Benjamin%20asked%20their%20wedding%20guests%20to