0a%20good%20experience.%20I%20didn't%20tell%20the%20university%20I%20was%20gone.%20After%20that%2C%20I%20was%20hooked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20to%20Colombia%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%202021%20and%20the%20Ivory%20Coast%20later%20that%20year.%20I%20committed%20to%20myself%20to%20go%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquiet-vacation-from-300k-wall-street-job-not-fulfilling-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equiet%20vacations%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20much%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20I%20went%20to%20Portugal%2C%20London%2C%20Barcelona%2C%20Sydney%2C%20and%20Ibiza.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2210a85524-ce0f-442e-ab64-f6e38665d9c8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20mom%20is%20a%20public%20school%20teacher%2C%20and%20the%20school%20district%20where%20she%20worked%20was%20desperate%20for%20teachers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20living%20on%20campus%20for%20a%20while%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20move%20out%20of%20Berkeley%20because%20I%20disliked%20the%20university%20vibe.%20I%20knew%20nobody%20would%20know%2C%20and%20it%20was%20cheaper%20to%20live%20in%20Oklahoma.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20to%20pick%20up%20another%20job%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fey-partner-quit-job-finance-math-teacher-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eteaching%20math%20to%2010th%20graders%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20my%20mom%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20the%20job%20as%20a%20public%20school%20teacher%20in%202022.%20I%20teach%20in%20person%20during%20the%20school%20year%20and%20travel%20during%20every%20school%20break.%20I%20take%20a%20big%20quiet%20vacation%20from%20the%20university%20during%20the%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22025933ca-847c-44be-bc47-fce6987cc6c6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20go%20on%20trips%20for%20professional%20development%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20give%20an%20hourlong%20talk%20as%20part%20of%20my%20research%20on%20digital%20nomadism.%20After%20these%20trips%2C%20I%20take%20a%20quiet%20vacation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%202022%2C%20I%20took%20an%20epic%20three-week%20trip%20to%20Antarctica.%20I%20used%20the%20majority%20of%20my%20leave%20from%20public%20school%20to%20go.%20Nobody%20at%20my%20university%20knew%20I%20was%20gone%20for%20that%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20I%20returned%20to%20the%20UK%20multiple%20times%20and%20spent%20the%20summer%20in%20Vienna%2C%20Barcelona%2C%20Portugal%2C%20Seville%2C%20and%20Paris.%20I%20went%20to%20Corfu%20for%20one%20week%20in%20October%2C%20and%20in%20December%2C%20I%20went%20to%20Cameroon%20for%20four%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20stay%20with%20my%20girlfriend%20in%20London%20and%20with%20family%20in%20Cameroon.%20If%20I'm%20not%20staying%20at%20a%20friend's%20house%2C%20I%20split%20an%20Airbnb%20with%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20man%20holding%20the%20Eiffel%20tower%20in%20the%20palm%20of%20his%20hands%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6723d592a0a0cc14f2255bbe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFields%20in%20Paris.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Benjamin%20Fields%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b3161e96-df8e-498e-b369-795886f91adb%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20use%202%20phones%20to%20quiet%20vacation%20successfully%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20phone%20number%20is%20my%20personal%20number.%20I%20have%20another%20phone%20number%20that%20handles%20all%20of%20my%20business%20stuff.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fdeals%2Fbest-vpn-deals%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20use%20a%20VPN%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20puts%20my%20location%20in%20San%20Francisco.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20use%20Google%20Fi%20as%20my%20cellphone%20provider%20because%20it%20gives%20me%20WiFi%20tethering%20and%20up%20to%2050%20GB%20of%20data%20worldwide.%20I%20can%20easily%20ru