e%20Trump%20administration%20would%20build%20millions%20of%20homes%20in%20part%20by%20making%20energy%20cheaper.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20drill%2C%20baby%2C%20drill%2C%20lower%20energy%20costs%2C%20and%20that's%20going%20to%20make%20it%20easier%20to%20build%20homes%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9pPCCh_t4h8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20an%20October%20campaign%20stop%20in%20Nevada.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHousing%20policy%20experts%20and%20economists%20disagree%2C%20saying%20lower%20energy%20costs%20would%20not%20significantly%20boost%20construction%20or%20make%20homes%20cheaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20new%20housing%20is%20largely%20determined%20by%20the%20availability%20of%20workers%2C%20the%20prices%20of%20building%20materials%2C%20and%20government%20regulations%20that%20limit%20construction.%20Other%20policies%20Trump%20has%20promised%20to%20enact%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0including%20hiking%20tariffs%20on%20a%20slew%20of%20foreign%20imports%20and%20deporting%20millions%20of%20immigrants%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0are%20expected%20to%20inflate%20housing%20costs%20by%20increasing%20the%20cost%20of%20key%20materials%20and%20worsening%20the%20labor%20shortage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Vance%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221a82d7c2-a275-42fb-a86a-4ae9f17818b1%5C%22%3EBuilding%20materials%20and%20tariffs%20outweigh%20cheaper%20oil%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEconomists%20say%20that%20lower%20electricity%20costs%20and%20diesel%20fuel%20prices%20would%20make%20certain%20goods%20and%20services%20needed%20to%20build%20housing%20somewhat%20cheaper.%20But%20they%20wouldn't%20dent%20the%20most%20significant%20input%20costs%20related%20to%20building%2C%20which%20are%20labor%20and%20building%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20saying%20it's%20immaterial%2C%26quot%3B%20Anirban%20Basu%2C%20chief%20economist%20at%20the%20construction%20industry%20trade%20group%20Associated%20Builders%20and%20Contractors%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BEnergy%20prices%20are%20significant%2C%20but%20they're%20not%20as%20significant%20as%20many%20other%20inputs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20prices%20of%20key%20building%20materials%2C%20including%20lumber%20and%20structural%20steel%2C%20are%20much%20more%20consequential.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20softwood%20lumber%20prices%20took%20off%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20it%20really%20impacted%20apartment%20construction%20and%20single-family%20home%20building%2C%26quot%3B%20Basu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20under%20the%20Biden%20administration%2C%20the%20US%20has%20produced%20and%20exported%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eia.gov%2Ftodayinenergy%2Fdetail.php%3Fid%3D61545%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20crude%20oil%20than%20ever%20before%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20country's%20history%2C%20even%20as%20housing%20costs%20have%20soared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETariffs%20imposed%20by%20both%20the%20Trump%20and%20Biden%20administrations%20on%20goods%20like%20Canadian%20lumber%20aren't%20helping%2C%20Andrew%20Justus%2C%20a%20housing%20policy%20analyst%20at%20the%20Niskanen%20Center%2C%20a%20nonpartisan%20think%20tank%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20And%20Trump%20has%20promised%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Ftrump-tariffs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edramatically%20hike%20tariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20he's%20elected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20think%20about%20what%20is%20specifically%20within%20the%20government's%20purview%2C%20as%20far%20as%20bringing%20down%20costs%20for%20building%20homes%2C%20one%20of%20the%20easiest%20things%20they%20could%20do%20is%20reduce%20the%20extra%20tax%20that%20they%20levy%20on%20the%20most%20basic%20of%20building%20materials%2C%26quot%3B%20Justus%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2249b4842e-9770-4c1e-a378-22cc2018c301%5C%22%3ELabor%20costs%20and%20cutting%20red%20tape%20are%20also%20key%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELabor%20costs%20are%20generally%20growing%20as%20a%20portion%20of%20overall%20construction%20costs%2C%20Basu%20said.%20This%20is%20largely%20a%20result%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-crisis-national-shortage-construction-workers-job-demand-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enational%20construction%20worker%20shortage%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20particularly%20among%20skilled%20workers%2C%20and%20lagging%20productivity%20in%20the%20industry.%20While%20labor%20productivity%20has%20improved%20in%20most%20sectors%20of%20the%20economy%20over%20the%20last%20half-century%2C%20US%20construction%20productivity%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.economist.com%2Fbusiness%2F2017%2F08%2F19%2Fefficiency-eludes-the-construction-industry%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20declined%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20look%20at%20a%20typical%20construction%20job%20site%2C%20it%20does%20not%20look%20that%20different%20from%20what%20it%20might've%20looked%20like%20five%20or%20six%20decades%20ago%2C%26quot%3B%20Basu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVance%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjd-vance-said-migrants-to-blame-for-expensive-homes-wrong-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealso%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Trump's%20plan%20to%20deport%20millions%20of%20immigrants%20would%20lower%20demand%20for%20housing%20and%2C%20thereby%2C%20slow%20rising%20home%20prices%20and%20rents.%20But%20economists%20say%20immigration%20isn't%20a%20major%20reason%20for%20higher%20housing%20costs%2C%20and%20because%20such%20a%20large%20portion%20of%20construction%20workers%20are%20immigrants%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F10%2F11%2Fbusiness%2Feconomy%2Ftrump-housing-crisis-deportations.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emass%20deportations%20would%20slow%20home%20construction%20and%20push