22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Bibek%20Debroy's%20Last%20NDTV%20Column%3A%20Why%20India%20Needs%20A%20New%20Poverty%20Line%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F5t1qoki8_rande_625x300_27_September_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20co-author%2C%20Bibek%20Debroy%2C%20passed%20away%20on%20November%201%20at%20the%20age%20of%2069.%20This%20is%20his%20last%20column%20for%20NDTV%2C%20which%20he%20submitted%20on%20October%2021.%20His%20other%20columns%20can%20be%20found%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fauthor%2Fbibek-debroy-aditya-sinha%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Global%20Multidimensional%20Poverty%20Index%20(MPI)%20is%20a%20comprehensive%20tool%20developed%20by%20the%20Oxford%20Poverty%20and%20Human%20Development%20Initiative%20(OPHI)%20and%20the%20UNDP's%20Human%20Development%20Report%20Office.%20It%20was%20first%20introduced%20in%202010%20to%20measure%20acute%20multidimensional%20poverty%20across%20over%20100%20developing%20countries.%20The%20MPI%20goes%20beyond%20income-based%20poverty%20measures%20by%20assessing%20deprivation%20across%20three%20key%20dimensions%3A%20health%2C%20education%2C%20and%20standard%20of%20living.%20These%20dimensions%20are%20represented%20through%20ten%20specific%20indicators%2C%20such%20as%20stunting%2C%20underweight%2C%20child%20mortality%2C%20years%20of%20schooling%2C%20and%20access%20to%20basic%20amenities%20like%20clean%20water%20and%20electricity.%20Each%20indicator%20is%20assigned%20a%20weight%2C%20with%20the%20health%20and%20education%20dimensions%20receiving%201%2F6%20weight%20each%2C%20and%20the%20standard%20of%20living%20indicators%20collectively%20weighted%20at%201%2F18%20each.%20Individuals%20are%20considered%20multidimensionally%20poor%20if%20they%20are%20deprived%20in%20at%20least%20one-third%20of%20the%20weighted%20indicators%2C%20emphasising%20the%20interconnectedness%20of%20deprivations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20MPI%20Is%20Calculated%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMethodologically%2C%20the%20MPI%20computation%20starts%20by%20constructing%20a%20deprivation%20profile%20for%20each%20household%20based%20on%20survey%20data%20such%20as%20Multiple%20Indicator%20Cluster%20Surveys%20and%20Demographic%20and%20Health%20Surveys.%20These%20profiles%20track%20deprivations%20for%20every%20individual%20in%20the%20household.%20The%20MPI%20is%20calculated%20as%20the%20product%20of%20the%20incidence%20(H)%2C%20or%20the%20proportion%20of%20people%20who%20are%20multidimensionally%20poor%2C%20and%20the%20intensity%20(A)%2C%20which%20measures%20the%20average%20share%20of%20deprivations%20experienced%20by%20the%20poor.%20This%20approach%20enables%20disaggregation%20of%20poverty%20data%20by%20region%2C%20age%20group%2C%20and%20other%20socio-demographic%20factors%2C%20allowing%20for%20more%20precise%20targeting%20of%20interventions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Multidimensional%20Poverty%20Index%20(MPI)%2C%20which%20considers%20various%20non-monetary%20deprivations%20across%20health%2C%20education%2C%20and%20living%20standards%2C%20reveals%20significant%20regional%20disparities.%20Sub-Saharan%20Africa%20and%20South%20Asia%20remain%20disproportionately%20affected%2C%20housing%2083%25%20of%20the%20world's%20poor.%20In%20countries%20with%20low%20Human%20Development%20Index%20(HDI)%20scores%2C%20such%20as%20Niger%2C%20Chad%2C%20and%20the%20Democratic%20Republic%20of%20the%20Congo%2C%20high%20poverty%20rates%20persist%2C%20with%20over%20half%20of%20the%20population%20living%20in%20multidimensional%20poverty.%20While%20global%20efforts%20have%20reduced%20poverty%2C%20particularly%20in%20countries%20like%20Nepal%20and%20Sierra%20Leone%2C%20challenges%20related%20to%20governance%2C%20conflict%2C%20and%20environmental%20shocks%20continue%20to%20hinder%20progress%20in%20many%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Some%20Regions%20Have%20Progressed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20challenges%2C%2076%20countries%20have%20witnessed%20statistically%20significant%20reductions%20in%20MPI%20values.%20Sub-Saharan%20Africa%2C%20despite%20housing%20the%20largest%20concentration%20of%20the%20poor%2C%20has%20seen%20notable%20improvements%20in%20countries%20such%20as%20Ethiopia%20and%20Liberia.%20These%20reductions%20are%20often%20attributed%20to%20strategic%20interventions%20in%20education%2C%20healthcare%2C%20and%20infrastructure%2C%20which%20address%20the%20core%20dimensions%20of%20multidimensional%20poverty.%20The%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20temporarily%20reversed%20gains%20in%20some%20areas%2C%20but%20post-pandemic%20data%20shows%20a%20slow%20resumption%20of%20progress%20in%20most%20regions.%20This%20highlights%20the%20need%20for%20sustained%2C%20evidence-based%20policy%20interventions%2C%20particularly%20in%20conflict-prone%20regions%20where%20poverty%20alleviation%20efforts%20have%20been%20stymied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20been%20a%20standout%20case%20in%20global%20poverty%20reduction%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20last%20decade.%20With%20234%20million%20people%20living%20in%20multidimensional%20poverty%20in%202024%2C%20India%20still%20accounts%20for%20the%20largest%20number%20of%20poor%20individuals%20globally.%20However%2C%20the%20country's%20efforts%20to%20address%20poverty%20through%20large-scale%20programmes%20have%20yielded%20impressive%20results.%20Since%202005-06%2C%20India%20has%20significantly%20reduced%20the%20MPI%2C%20with%20a%2016.4%20percentage%20point%20reduction%20in%20poverty%20incidence%20between%202015-16%20and%202019-20%20alone.%20Programmes%20such%20as%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Awas%20Yojana%20(housing)%2C%20Swachh%20Bharat%20Abhiyan%20(sanitation)%2C%20and%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20(healthcare)%20have%20targeted%20the%20core%20deprivations%20affecting%20millions%2C%20particularly%20in%20rural%20areas%20where%20poverty%20is%20most%20prevalent.%20Substantial%20improvements%20in%20key%20indicators%20such%20as%20nutrition%2C%20school%20attendance%2C%20and%20access%20to%20electricity%20have%20driven%20India's%20multidimensional%20poverty%20reduction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMPI%20Is%20Inadequate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20is%20MPI%20a%20real%20measure%20of%20poverty%3F%20The%20answer%20is%20no.%20It%20is%20more%20of%20a%20development%20indicator%20rather%20than%20a%20true%20measure%20of%20poverty.%20As%20discussed%2C%20MDPI%20is%20grounded%20in%20three%20key%20dimensions%3A%20health%2C%20education%2C%20and%20living%20standards.%20Health%20indicators%E2%80%94such%20as%20nutrition%2C%20child%20and%20adolescent%20mortality%2C%20and%20maternal%20health%E2%80%94along%20with%20education%20metrics%20like%20years%20of%20schooling%20and%20school%20attendance%20are%20undeniably%20crucial%20for%20shaping%20an%20individual's%20future%20prospects%20and%20determining%20long-term%20poverty%20outcomes.%20These%20dimensions%2C%20however%2C%20are%20more%20forward-looking%20in%20nature%20and%20capture%20the%20potential%20for%20future%20poverty%20rather%20than%20the%20immediate%20deprivation%20that%20living%20standards%20reflect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELiving%20standards%20encompass%20access%20to%20cooking%20fuel%2C%20sanitation%2C%20drinking%20water%2C%20electricity%2C%20housing%2C%20assets%2C%20and%20financial%20inclusion%20(e.g.%2C%20bank%20accounts)%2C%20providing%20a%20more%20immediate%20and%20tangible%20picture%20of%20poverty.%20While%20health%20and%20education%20are%20critical%20drivers%20of%20development%2C%20conflating%20them%20with%20living%20standards%20under%20the%20umbrella%20of%20%E2%80%9Cpoverty%E2%80%9D%20risks%20diluting%20the%20focus%20of%20poverty%20measurement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20this%20elasticity%20is%20necessary%20because%20poverty%20is%20not%20just%20about%20material%20deprivation%3B%20it%20also%20encompasses%20missed%20opportunities%20and%20structural%20disadvantages.%20As%20Sen%20(1999)%20and%20Nussbaum%20(2000)%20highlight%20in%20their%20capabilities%20approach%2C%20addressing%20poverty%20requires%20more%20than%20just%20economic%20relief%E2%80%94it%20demands%20empowering%20individuals%20to%20lead%20lives%20they%20value%2C%20which%20involves%20access%20to%20education%20and%20health.%20In%20this%20sense%2C%20the%20broad%20scope%20of%20MDPI%20reflects%20a%20deeper%20understanding%20of%20human%20development%20and%20the%20interrelatedness%20of%20various%20deprivations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20The%20Tendulkar%20Line%20Is%20Outdated%20Now%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20we%20need%20an%20updated%20headcount%20ratio%20to%20accurately%20measure%20poverty%20and%20assess%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20its%20socio-economic%20policies.%20India%20also%20urgently%20needs%20a%20new%20poverty%20line%20due%20to%20the%20outdated%20nature%20of%20the%20existing%20Tendulkar%20line%2C%20last%20updated%20in%202011-12.%20As%20economies%20evolve%2C%20so%20do%20the%20standards%20of%20what%20constitutes%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbare%20minimum%E2%80%9D%20for%20subsistence%2C%20yet%20India%20continues%20to%20rely%20on%20this%20decade-old%20benchmark.%20The%20debate%20over%20the%20adequacy%20of%20the%20%E2%82%B932%20per%20capita%20per%20day%20figure%2C%20once%20a%20lightning%20rod%20for%20controversy%2C%20highlights%20the%20need%20for%20a%20more%20accurate%20measure%20that%20reflects%20current%20economic%20realities.%20While%20the%20Rangarajan%20Committee%20proposed%20a%20revised%20poverty%20line%20in%202014%2C%20it%20was%20never%20officially%20adopted%2C%20leaving%20India%20reliant%20on%20an%20obsolete%20metric.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20release%20of%20new%20data%20from%20the%20Household%20Consumption%20Expenditure%20Survey%20(HCES)%2C%20there%20is%20an%20opportunity%20to%20recalibrate%20India's%20poverty%20line%20to%20reflect%20contemporary%20socio-economic%20conditions.%20The%20HCES%20provides%20detailed%20insights%20into%20household%20consumption%20patterns%2C%20and%20applying%20this%20data%20to%20a%20revised%20poverty%20line%20could%20give%20a%20more%20accurate%20measure%20of%20deprivation%20in%20the%20country.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Bibek%20Debroy%20was%20Chairman%2C%20Economic%20Advisory%20Council%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20and%20Aditya%20Sinha%20is%20OSD%2C%20Research%2C%20Economic%20Advisory%20Council%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20authors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730449740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2F5t1qoki8_rande_625x300_27_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-need-for-a-new-poverty-line-in-india-bibek-debroys-last-ndtv-column-6920513%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20the%20release%20of%20new%20data%20from%20the%20Household%20Consumption%20Expenditure%20Survey%20(HCES)%2C%20there%20is%20an%20opportunity%20to%20recalibrate%20India's%20poverty%20line%20to%20reflect%20contemporary%20socio-economic%20conditions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-need-for-a-new-poverty-line-in-india-bibek-debroys-last-ndtv-column-6920513%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Bhool%20Bhulaiyaa%203'%20gets%20strong%20start%20at%20BO%20with%20Rs%209.14%20cr%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730449728000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-114842683%2Cimgsize-90324.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fbox-office%2Fbhool-bhulaiyaa-3-off-to-a-