%20genuine%20inspiration.%20The%20film%20throws%20in%20scenes%20from%20mythology%20-%20a%20narrator%20links%20one%20episode%20to%20another%20-%20to%20serve%20as%20parallels%20to%20the%20events%20unfolding%20in%20present%20times.%20The%20connection%20sought%20to%20be%20forged%20between%20myth%20and%20reality%20is%20overly%20stilted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20tank%20is%20as%20alarmingly%20leaky%20as%20this%20and%20the%20game%20hinges%20on%20tricks%20that%20are%20well%20past%20their%20sell-by%20dates%2C%20it%20is%20the%20most%20convenient%20thing%20to%20fall%20back%20on%20Hindi%20cinema's%20go-to%20storehouse%20of%20ideas%20and%20characters%20-%20the%20Ramayan.%20But%20even%20the%20Lord%20cannot%20salvage%20%3Cem%3ESingham%20Again%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20arrows%20in%20the%20film's%20quiver%20are%20blunt.%20Big%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20decade%20after%20Ajay%20Devgn's%20swaggering%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20Bajirao%20Singham%20went%20after%20the%20evil%20empire%20of%20a%20sham%20godman%20in%20%3Cem%3ESingham%20Returns%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20he%20returns%20again%20in%20%3Cem%3ESingham%20Again%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20wage%20a%20cross-border%20war%20against%20a%20terrorist%2C%20Danger%20Lanka%20alias%20Zubair%20Hafeez%20(Arjun%20Kapoor).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20evil%20man%20isn't%20waging%20a%20religious%20war.%20He%20is%20instead%20on%20a%20personal%20mission%20to%20avenge%20his%20father%20and%20uncles%20and%20free%20his%20grandfather%20Omar%20Hafeez%20(Jackie%20Shroff)%20from%20a%20high-security%20Indian%20prison.%20He%20decides%20to%20use%20Singham's%20wife%20Avni%20(Kareena%20Kapoor%20Khan)%20as%20a%20bargaining%20chip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20another%20matter%20that%20the%20lady%20is%20a%20woman%20of%20substance%2C%20a%20culture%20ministry%20official%20who%20conceptualises%20and%20executes%20a%20new-age%20version%20of%20the%20Ram%20Leela.%20Shouldn't%20she%20be%20equipped%20to%20give%20as%20good%20as%20she%20gets%3F%20But%20no%2C%20that%20would%20defeat%20the%20very%20purpose%20of%20the%20film.%20So%2C%20she%20is%20projected%20as%20hapless%20and%20vulnerable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FMD7v0-igVIM%3Fsi%3DDqJGglqItwoFEaAQ%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20Ram-Sita-Ravana%20redux%2C%20the%20action%20hero%20dons%20the%20stale%20garb%20of%20a%20saviour-crusader%20out%20to%20right%20the%20wrongs%20perpetrated%20by%20a%20venal%20villain%20who%20is%20initially%20taken%20for%20a%20mere%20drug%20lord.%20A%20massacre%20and%20a%20kidnap%20later%2C%20Singham%20realises%20that%20he%20is%20dealing%20with%20a%20vicious%20psychopath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20might%20more%20easily%20locate%20a%20needle%20in%20a%20haystack%20than%20find%20any%20semblance%20of%20novelty%20in%20the%20plot%20that%20the%20maximalist%20cop%20drama%20peddles.%20The%20weaving%20of%20Ramayan%20references%20into%20a%20rough%20and%20ready%20good-versus-evil%20construct%2C%20besides%20being%20neither%20intriguing%20as%20an%20idea%20nor%20particularly%20heft-generating%20as%20a%20plot%20device%2C%20is%20marred%20by%20a%20doggedly%20trite%20approach%20to%20familiar%20conventions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20there%20isn't%20much%20by%20way%20originality%20in%20the%20screenplay%20authored%20by%20six%20writers%20(including%20director%20Rohit%20Shetty)%2C%20%3Cem%3ESingham%20Again%3C%2Fem%3E%20ropes%20in%20a%20phalanx%20of%20lawmen%20and%20a%20lawwoman%20(Deepika%20Padukone%2C%20who%20makes%20a%20promising%20entry%20into%20a%20male-dominated%20universe%20but%20isn't%20granted%20any%20opportunity%20to%20upstage%20her%20male%20co-actors)%20for%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Devgn%20slipped%20into%20the%20ballistic%20franchise-defining%20%26quot%3Baata%20majhi%20satakli%26quot%3B%20mode%20in%202011's%20%3Cem%3ESingham%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20lead%20actor%20was%20nearly%20a%20decade%20and%20a%20half%20younger.%20The%20grand%20acts%20of%20valour%20and%20daredevilry%20that%20he%20performed%20were%20in%20sync%20with%20director%20Shetty's%20vision%20of%20an%20invincible%20police%20officer%20so%20single-mindedly%20wedded%20to%20his%20job%20that%20he%20knew%20no%20fear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20is%20now%20older%20and%20a%20role%20model%20to%20peers%20and%20juniors%20alike%2C%20but%20the%20courageous%20cop%20still%20has%20jeeps%2C%20off-roaders%20and%20buildings%20going%20up%20in%20flames%20around%20him%20-%20the%20trademark%20of%20the%20directorial%20style%20that%20has%20been%20sustained%20with%20varying%20degrees%20of%20success%20in%20three%20other%20films%20of%20the%20franchise%20(%3Cem%3ESingham%20Returns%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3ESimmba%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3ESooryavanshi%3C%2Fem%3E).%20The%20appeal%20of%20Shetty's%20%26quot%3Baction%20design%26quot%3B%20has%20worn%20thin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20the%20fifth%20instalment%20of%20the%20Rohit%20Shetty%20Cop%20Universe%20franchise%2C%20everything%20is%20sought%20to%20be%20rendered%20with%20much%20greater%20flourish%20than%20ever%20before.%20But%20all%20the%20sanctimonious%20pomposity%20proves%20counter-productive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFans%20of%20the%20genre%20might%20be%20pleased%20by%20the%20overdose%20of%20bravado%20and%20rhetoric%20that%20flow%20out%20of%20the%20storyline%20and%20create%20room%20for%20cameos%20not%20just%20by%20%3Cem%3ESimmba%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3ESooryavanshi%3C%2Fem%3E%20but%20also%20by%20Salman%20Khan's%20Chulbul%20Pandey%2C%20creature%20of%20a%20different%20realm%20and%20sensibility%20(who%20pops%20up%20in%20a%20mid-credits%20scene%20to%20provide%20a%20glimpse%20of%20what%20might%20be%20on%20the%20way%20in%20this%20universe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBajirao%20Singham%20is%2C%20of%20course%2C%20the%20upright%20one%2C%20the%20one%20that%20nobody%20can%20stop%20when%20he%20loses%20his%20cool.%20He%20is%20Lord%20Ram.%20He%20is%20insuperable.%20The%20male%20cops%20around%20him%20are%20each%20given%20stereotypical%20traits.%20DCP%20Veer%20Sooryavanshi%20(Akshay%20Kumar)%2C%20a%20present-day%20personification%20of%20Garuda%20who%20arrives%20hanging%20from%20a%20chopper%2C%20is%20earnest%20to%20a%20fault%20but%20gets%20into%20a%20tangle%20with%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EACP%20Sangram%20Bhalerao%20alia%20Simmba%20(Ranveer%20Singh)%20is%20a%20Mumbai%20street%20lingo-spouting%2C%20wisecracking%20Monkey%20God%20who%20revels%20in%20jumping%20into%20tight%20spots%20grinning%20from%20ear%20to%20ear.%20And%20ACP%20Satya%20Bali%20(Tiger%20Shroff)%20is%20the%20young%20eager-beaver%20Lakshman%20always%20willing%20to%20learn%20at%20the%20feet%20of%20the%20past%20master%20who%20now%20has%20three%20films%20to%20his%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actors%2C%20led%20by%20Ajay%20Devgn%20treading%20tried%20and%20tested%20terrain%2C%20do%20their%20bit%2C%20Ranveer%20Singh%20a%20little%20more%20than%20the%20others.%20However%2C%20even%20when%20all%20the%20bits%20are%20added%20up%2C%20the%20payoff%20is%20minuscule.%20The%20trouble%20is%20they%20aren't%20required%20to%20act.%20They%20either%20strut%20about%20like%20models%20on%20a%20catwalk%2C%20deliver%20stuffy%20lines%20about%20duty%20and%20morality%20or%20attempt%20to%20provide%20comic%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20far%20the%20brightest%20spark%20in%C2%A0%3Cem%3ESingham%20Again%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20Ranveer%20Singh.%20With%20his%20constant%20chatter%2C%20he%20is%20indeed%20funny%20for%20the%20most%20part.%20There%20is%20little%20else%20in%20%3Cem%3ESingham%20Again%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20would%20enthuse%20the%20audience%20to%20intone%20%26quot%3Bencore%26quot%3B%20in%20unison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepika%20Padukone's%20character%20-%20whatever%20I%20have%20learnt%20I%20have%20learnt%20from%20you%2C%20she%20says%20more%20than%20once%20to%20Bajirao%20Singham%20-%20definitely%20deserves%20a%20whole%20film%