ion-final-ruling-scotus-roe-v-wade-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERoe%20v.%20Wade%3C%2Fa%3E%20being%20overturned...%20Everything%20just%20kind%20of%20piled%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fuvalde-shooting%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eschool%20shooting%20in%20Uvalde%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202022%2C%20where%20a%20teenage%20gunman%20fatally%20shot%2019%20children%20and%20two%20teachers%2C%20Turner%20said%20she%20%26quot%3Bknew%20it%20was%20time%20to%20get%20the%20fuck%20out%20of%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20she%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vogue.co.uk%2Farticle%2Fsophie-turner-british-vogue-interview%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBritish%20Vogue%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20at%20the%20time%2C%20she%20felt%20like%20a%20%26quot%3Blittle%20bird%20trapped%20in%20a%20gilded%20cage%26quot%3B%20living%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20couldn't%20fathom%20being%20a%20mother%20of%20one%20of%20those%20children%20knowing%20that%20this%20was%20something%20your%20country%20could%20fix%2C%20that%20they'd%20rather%20have%20rights%20to%20guns%20than%20give%20kids%20a%20right%20to%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMeanwhile%2C%20women%20in%20the%20US%20are%20being%20stripped%20of%20their%20rights%2C%20left%2C%20right%20and%20center.%20It%20all%20contributed%20to%20this%20feeling%20of%20I%20have%20to%20get%20out%2C%20I%20have%20to%20get%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3BGame%20of%20Thrones%26quot%3B%20actor%20and%20Jonas%20announced%20their%20plan%20to%20divorce%20last%20year.%20They%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjoe-jonas-sophie-turner-children-daughters-parenting-facts-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshare%20two%20daughters%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Willa%2C%204%2C%20and%20Delphine%2C%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETurner%2C%20who%