r%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Sharma%20wrote%20in%20his%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETake%20a%20look%20below%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAndroid%20vs%20iOS%20-%20different%20prices%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFlipkart%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40Flipkart%3C%2Fa%3E%20App%3F%3F%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cnsame%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmy_mokobara%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40my_mokobara%3C%2Fa%3E%20cabin%20suitcase%20costs%204119%E2%82%B9%20on%20FK%20Android%20App%20vs%204799%E2%82%B9%20on%20iOS%20App.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnApple%20charges%2030%25%20commission%20on%20subscriptions%20etc%2C%20so%20different%20pricing%20for%20iOS%20makes%20sense%20there.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnBut%20for%20ecommerce%3F%20Very%20shady%20%26amp%3B%20unfair.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FYmIq8nhuXO%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FYmIq8nhuXO%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Saurabh%20Sharma%20(%40randomusements)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frandomusements%2Fstatus%2F1851503526125666544%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2030%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20following%20post%2C%20Mr%20Sharma%20shared%20a%20screenshot%20of%20a%20conversation%20he%20had%20with%20Flipkart%20customer%20support.%20The%20e-commerce%20site%20explained%2C%20%E2%80%9CPrices%20may%20vary%20since%20it%20is%20determined%20by%20the%20seller%20based%20on%20various%20factors.%20However%2C%20please%20don't%20worry%2C%20our%20sellers%20are%20always%20trying%20their%20best%20to%20bring%20you%20great%20deals%20and%20discounts.%20Happy%20shopping!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sharma%20shared%20the%20post%20on%20Wednesday.%20Since%20then%20it%20has%20garnered%20more%20than%20127%2C000%20views%20and%20several%20comments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20post%2