%20Whitewater%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20water%20utility%20venture%20that%20converts%20treated%20water%20from%20sewage%20treatment%20plants%20(STPs)%20into%20high-quality%20potable%20water%20%E2%80%94%20has%20partnered%20with%20the%20non-profit%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F173853%2Fbengaluru-ground-water-crisis-well-digging-day-zero-zenrainman%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBiome%20Environmental%20Trust%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20launch%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20indirect%20potable%20water%20reuse%20project.%20This%20innovative%20initiative%2C%20located%20in%20Devanahalli%2C%2040%20kilometres%20northeast%20of%20Bengaluru%2C%20uses%20managed%20aquifer%20recharge%20to%20achieve%20sustainable%20water%20reuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20participants%20%5Bof%20this%20project%5D%2C%20the%20project%20produces%206.4%20lakh%20litres%20of%20potable%20drinking%20water%20per%20day%2C%20adhering%20to%20BIS%20(Bureau%20of%20Indian%20Standards)-10500%20standards.%20The%20clean%20water%20directly%20benefits%20thousands%20of%20residents%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F139499%2Fdevanahalli-toilets-karnataka-odf-fstp-swachh-bharat%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDevanahalli%20%3C%2Fa%3Emunicipality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20does%20this%20work%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimply%20put%2C%20treated%20wastewater%20from%20a%20sewage%20treatment%20plant%20is%20first%20pumped%20into%20Bagalur%20Lake%2C%20where%20it%20is%20diluted%20with%20rainwater.%20This%20water%20is%20then%20directed%20to%20Devanahalli%E2%80%99s%20Sihineeru%20Kere%20Lake%20through%20a%20pipeli