ow%20diabetes%20can%20impact%20their%20overall%20health.%20Then%2C%20we%20guide%20them%20on%20the%20lifestyle%20changes%20they%20must%20make%20after%20a%20diagnosis%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Deshpande%20shares.%20Endocrinology%20concerns%20become%20especially%20crucial%20to%20treat%20in%20cases%20of%20pregnancy.%20So%20it%20is%20fortunate%2C%20Dr%20Deshpande%20smiles%2C%20that%20the%20gynaecology%20unit%20is%20just%20next%20door.%20All%20pregnant%20patients%20are%20advised%20a%20complete%20blood%20workup%2C%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20vitamin%20levels%20and%20thyroid%20hormone%20levels%20(TSH).%20Any%20imbalance%20is%20treated%20through%20medicines%2C%20diet%2C%20and%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FLT-2-1730121810.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20medical%20equipment%20at%20L%26amp%3BT%E2%80%99s%20Andheri%20health%20centre%20is%20state-of-art%20as%20are%20the%20operation%20theatres%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FLT-2-1730121810.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FLT-2-1730121810-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FLT-2-1730121810-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FLT-2-1730121810-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FLT-2-1730121810-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-372662%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20medical%20equipment%20at%20L%26amp%3BT%E2%80%99s%20Andheri%20health%20centre%20is%20state-of-art%20as%20are%20the%20operation%20theatres.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERucha%20Pa