nology%2C%20including%20X-rays%2C%20ultrasound%2C%20dental%20equipment%2C%20and%20equipment%20deployed%20in%20scopies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Madhuri%20Franklin%2C%20who%20is%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20the%20operations%20at%20the%20Andheri%20centre%2C%20lets%20us%20in%20on%20the%20know-how%20of%20spearheading%20a%20project%20of%20this%20scope.%20The%20work%20is%20extensive%2C%20but%20she%20credits%20her%20drive%20to%20the%20satisfaction%20she%20derives%20from%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FxhChRC5wr8k%3Fsi%3DTa41NHAm0XHc6YMJ%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Dr%20Franklin%20whose%20professional%20trajectory%20has%20been%20coloured%20with%20experience%20in%20public%20health%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%2C%20taking%20charge%20of%20this%20project%20is%20almost%20like%20a%20return%20to%20the%20roots.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20previous%20experience%20made%20me%20aware%20of%20the%20gaps%20in%20healthcare%20in%20the%20community%20at%20large.%20I%20can%20say%20with%20certainty%20that%20going%20to%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20doorsteps%20with%20services%20makes%20a%20difference.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shares%20an%20observation%20of%20the%20uptick%20in%20the%20number%20of%20people%20who%20seek%20assistance%20in%20family%20planning%20and%20opt%20for%20sterilisation%20procedures%20at%20the%20centre.%20Consulting%20gynaecologist%20Dr%20Shreya%20Prabhoo%20reasons%20this%20increase.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20are%20starting%20to%20become%20more%20cognisant%20of%20family%20planning.%20Earlier%20people%20were%20under%20the%20impression%20that%20female%20sterilisation%20was%20the%20only%20approach.%20Male%20sterilisation%20is%20a%20big%20taboo%20in%20our%20society%2C%20you%20see.%20It%20is%20assumed%20that%20the%20man%20will%20lose%20his%20libido%20or%20%E2%80%98manhood%E2%80%99%20after%20a%20vasectomy%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20through%20extensive%20education%20that%20dispels%20these%20misconceptions%2C%20the%20doctors%20are%20starting%20to%20see%20a%20shift%20in%20attitudes.%20The%20statistics%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Andheri%20centre%20has%20completed%2055%2C000%20family%20planning%20surgeries%20%E2%80%94%20are%20a%20nod%20to%20these%20mindset%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EQuality%20healthcare%20at%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20doorstep%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20state-of-the-art%20services%20and%20consultations%20are%20made%20available%20to%20the%20patients%20who%20head%20to%20the%20L%26amp%3BT%20centres%2C%20there%20was%20a%20burgeoning%20need%20to%20extend%20the%20same%20to%20those%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20this%20privilege.%20This%20gap%20is%20bridged%20by%20the%20Mobile%20Health%20Units%2C%20which%20take%20medical%20services%20to%20the%20urban%2C%20peri-urban%2C%20as%20well%20as%20far-flung%20rural%20and%20tribal%20poor%2C%20explains%20Dahlia%20Sengupta%2C%20a%20volunteer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%2015%20years%20Sengupta%20has%20co-ordinated%20this%20enormous%20exercise%20that%20provides%20services%20to%20beneficiaries%20from%20rural%20communities%20within%20a%20short%20radius%20of%20where%20they%20live.%20Through%20weekly%2C%20monthly%20and%20need-based%20interventions%2C%20these%20mobile%20health%20units%20reach%20out%20to%20slum%20areas%20spread%20across%20Mumbai%20city%2C%20Navi%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20Thane.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20%5Bslum%20dwellers%5D%20do%20not%20have%20the%20time%20to%20take%20a%20break%20from%20their%20work%20and%20head%20to%20the%20health%20centres%20for%20a%20check-up%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sengupta%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201720px)%20100vw%2C%201720px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fupload