e%20of%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20both%20the%20sector%20and%20the%20CCIs%20from%20which%20these%20youths%20transition.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99re%20constantly%20working%20to%20bridge%20the%20gap%20between%20what%E2%80%99s%20available%20and%20what%E2%80%99s%20needed%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20about%20much%20more%20than%20just%20providing%20shelter%20%E2%80%94%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20creating%20opportunities%20for%20growth%2C%20healing%2C%20and%20independence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUnity%20through%20diversity%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYouth%20find%20their%20way%20to%20WeLive%20through%20a%20dynamic%20outreach%20programme%2C%20explains%20Prithvi%20Shukla%2C%20programme%20manager%20at%20the%20NGO.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20established%20a%20national%20care%20leavers%20association%20and%20work%20closely%20with%20district%20child%20protection%20officers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20partner%20with%20agencies%20and%20visit%20various%20CCIs%2C%20where%20we%20introduce%20our%20programme%2C%20explain%20its%20components%2C%20and%20demonstrate%20how%20we%20operate.%20Many%20of%20these%20young%20individuals%20are%20uncertain%20about%20their%20future%2C%20and%20the%20value%20of%20what%20we%20offer%20often%20resonates%20with%20CCIs.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20our%20outreach%20%E2%80%94%20our%20alumni%20have%20begun%20referring%20friends%20as%20well%2C%20creating%20a%20growing%20network.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FWelive-2nd-Year-Annual-Day-230_11zon-1729768383.jpg%3Ffit%3D1122%252C748%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221122%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22WeLive%20has%20a%20diverse%20group%20with%20youth%20speaking%20more%20than%20five%20different%20languages.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22http